text: Henrietta High School is a public high school located in Henrietta, Texas (USA). It is the sole high school in the Henrietta Independent School District. In 2015, the school was rated "Met Standard" by the Texas Education Agency. ==Athletics== The Henrietta Bearcats compete in the following sports: *Baseball *Basketball *Cross Country *Football *Golf *Powerlifting *Softball *Tennis *Track and Field *Volleyball ==References== == External links == * Official Website Category:Schools in Clay County, Texas Category:Public high schools in Texas
title: Henrietta High School
